~ phone
Pay Phone: *briiiing* You pick up the receiver. It's warm.
Mom: Hi sweetie! You sound far away. Want me to write down where you are, in case you faint again?
- Yes, save my progress => do_save
- Not right now => hangup

~ do_save
do GameState.save_game()
Mom: Got it, scribbled on the fridge. Be safe out there! And eat a vegetable.
=> END

~ hangup
Mom: Okay. ...You never call, you know. Bye-bye!
=> END
